4 March 2009Government will hold Cluster media briefings on the implementation of the Government s Programme of Action for 2009 in Pretoria from 2 to 13 March 2009.The briefings will take place at Room 153, Union Buildings, Pretoria.There will be a video link-up to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Briefing scheduleThursday, 5 March 200911h00-12h30: Justice, Crime, Security and Prevention Cluster ( Chair: Minister of Safety and Security)Monday, 9 March 2009: 09h00-10h30: Social Cluster (Chair: Minister of Health)Tuesday, 10 March 200912h00-13h30: Economic, Investment and Employment Cluster (Chair: Minister of Trade and Industry)Thursday, 12 March09h00-10h30: Governance and Administration Cluster (Chair: Minister of Public Service &amp; Administration )NB: The date for the International Relations, Peace and Security Cluster is still to be confirmedEnquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)